{"tid":1481532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒絕攬炒？","createTime":"2019-08-17T17:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:43:33.000Z","uid":296350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7607949f0c35721c2bcf6862830011c8ee48945a","tid":1481532,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"拒絕攬炒？<br />\n企喺對面/扮中立/漠不關心/只係因為懶同怕辛苦嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">你</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n知唔知咩叫攬炒？<br />\n係玉石俱焚/係一鑊熟/係攬住一齊死呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">有前線係寫咗遺書上戰場架！！</span></span></strong><br />\n你見唔見到佢哋嘅絕望同決心？你覺得佢哋會輕言放棄？會驚？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">佢地贏就係你輸！<br />\n佢哋輸就係攬炒！<br />\n你根本冇機會贏！<br />\n你贏即係攬炒！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同佢地一齊贏定一齊輸！<br />\n你自己揀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">想拒絕攬炒就一齊贏<br />\n聽日港島見</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n#818維園 #香港人 #拒絕攬炒 #攬炒"},{"pid":"c65383931b972f18e7c49c8c893151ac438a9fb1","tid":1481532,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:53:07.000Z","msg":"明天見"},{"pid":"c2f74248e2a06cdb428ed3f363a3894d46956089","tid":1481532,"uid":295572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"[有IG嘅同我入黎] 捍衛自己地盤啊diu<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481523</a><br />\n有時間幫手diu zau 5 mo!"},{"pid":"a61fdf59bd3da6029a86bc0128fd8d563e6cd98e","tid":1481532,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:21:15.000Z","msg":"818<br />\nYat Chai Yang"},{"pid":"dbd3ff6f0a0d8df30d61675e42e6aa62293e5f07","tid":1481532,"uid":224104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:14:10.000Z","msg":"觀念正確<br />\n概本就無攬炒以外既選擇"},{"pid":"2f6362caa5ef60c7b4c